Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.55,0:00:06.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,結果 可能是太過於喜歡自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.78,0:00:13.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也討厭被定性的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.50,0:00:18.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,個性之類的 也沒人需要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:24.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒人需要就沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.69,0:00:26.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有理由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.85,0:00:30.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被人需要什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.21,0:00:32.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很愉悅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.02,0:00:34.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,皆川同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.06,0:00:36.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,皆川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:39.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,皆川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.78,0:00:41.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你掉了東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.05,0:00:43.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以前就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:48.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他是當時我的朋友暗戀的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:53.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾覺得他們真相襯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.73,0:00:57.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.84,0:01:01.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,同時 那應當出現的協調感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.19,0:01:05.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,卻非常不融洽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.65,0:01:10.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 發了一下呆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:16.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是對齊藤同學有些什麼興趣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.53,0:01:21.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可能只是對「齊藤同學對我的好意」有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.96,0:01:24.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,於是就手滑試了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.71,0:01:26.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:38.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊 剛才逃開了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.83,0:01:41.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只是吃了一驚而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:44.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩人真是很相襯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:49.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 完全 沒有關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:52.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今後也要做好朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.12,0:01:56.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那一刻 我身體裡湧現出來的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:58.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,並不是罪惡感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.75,0:02:02.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也並非是膚淺的優越感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:08.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算死也不要像這樣成為
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:10.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,「被榨取的一方」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.06,0:02:17.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起來從那天起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.72,0:02:20.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,覺醒了「榨取的快感」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.29,0:02:23.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很好嗎 稍微像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:25.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很羨慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:29.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡上自己以外的別人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:32.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不可能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.86,0:02:33.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.02,0:02:35.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:37.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,醒著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:39.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 寺內君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:42.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,之前和你交往的那個女朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:44.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？早就分手了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:48.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼吃醋了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:52.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 沒有人能證明這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:56.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是個「有魅力的人」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:03:00.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吶吶 起來了不那個什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:06.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明天還要早起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.16,0:03:16.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺 沒熱情了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:24.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是沒有人說「好」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:26.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就不知道有多好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:31.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 又在看著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:35.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真有這麼喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:37.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對鐘井老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:41.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個 皆川老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:47.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,放學後 你有時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:50.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…就一會兒 行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:55.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喝杯茶 聊個天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.41,0:03:58.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:01.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:05.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還剩下一些不得不做的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:07.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那改天…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:08.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:12.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,放學後在音樂室裡聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:15.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 不是今天的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:19.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:21.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你會過來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:34.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安樂岡 花火同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,---------------op -----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:34.12,Kuzu_scene2,,0,0,0,,{\b1\pos(1032,579)}你可不行啊。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:57.48,Kuzu_scene2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,743)\pos(1032,579)}你可不行啊。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:16.93,Kuzu_scene1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(417,458)\blur7.5\t(0,417,\blur0)\t(4922,5380,\blur7.5)\t(417,4922,\fs82.5)\pos(1083,561)}我覺得這就是命運。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭宋_GBK\fs75\pos(975,693)\fad(0,1100)}什麼都沒做不是嗎。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:59.89,Kuzu_scene1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\fs90\fad(900,900)\c&H4B4B4B&\pos(1064,404.667)}三個月前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:12.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天一起的那個人是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:14.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老師的男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:19.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欸嘿嘿 討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:22.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:27.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,…的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:28.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安樂岡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:31.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安樂岡花火同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:46.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是僅僅在無意中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:48.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,變成我這樣的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:00.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,無意中？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:04.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 只是裝作沒有發覺而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:12.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你如此地毫無防備
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:14.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很吸引人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:18.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你最喜歡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:20.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,鐘井老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:23.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…哦…皆川老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:28.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你好 安樂岡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:31.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的不可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:34.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,請…請問有何貴幹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:35.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.75,0:07:36.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也並不是特別地覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:41.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,鐘井老師什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的菜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:38.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:41.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}你有東西忘在辦公室了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:42.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}給 文件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:45.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}十…十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:53.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是想看到你受傷的表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:02.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以更多地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:06.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,更多更多地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:09.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我看多點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:11.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:21.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安樂岡同學 放學後繼續 在音樂教室裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:25.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:27.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好想快點看到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:30.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,「被榨取的你」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:35.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,…的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:47.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡自己還是討厭自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:50.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,自身並沒有如此強烈的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:52.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要說的話就是普通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:54.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得很無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:56.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,像我這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:00.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在世時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:04.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也許是最高興看見我成為教師的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:06.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已經早就不在人世
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:10.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,隨年歲日漸淡忘的記憶中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:12.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩那長髮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:14.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能讓我清晰地想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:19.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對 不錯 正是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在春天裡 對某人一見鍾情什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:41.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我還真是單純啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:45.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 櫻花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.36,0:09:49.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天早上也見過面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:50.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:53.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像你沒發現呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:57.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才典禮的時候也有見到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:10:01.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天起我們都是新人了 請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:03.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這也太過於湊巧了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:05.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,正因太湊巧了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 你的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:10.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫皆川茜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:15.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得這就是命運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:22.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,鐘井老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:24.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,遲到了真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.97,0:10:30.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:31.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:38.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要說的話 是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:45.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊算了 全部 一切全都說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:46.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,輕鬆點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:49.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,總比沒說出來就完結的好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.22,0:10:52.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:53.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:56.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:28.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,眼淚流不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:31.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 這不是理所當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:33.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我沒有哭的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:35.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:41.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:42.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,努力過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:45.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他們會交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:47.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真討厭吶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:51.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,之後每天都要看到這幅景象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:54.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算這樣 明明都明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:57.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然明白 雖然事已至此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:58.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還是不想聽見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:02.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,反正即使在等待著也總有一天會知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:05.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼為什麼不說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:08.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明一直都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:11.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為一直都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:12.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:15.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:20.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕 他不再是我的哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:23.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:26.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因為這樣才會被搶走的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:37.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥知道的話肯定也會感到痛苦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.10,0:12:39.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過總是會知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:45.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:49.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在只是想依賴麥而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:51.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不能因為我自己的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:55.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就成為可以去傷害麥的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.99,0:13:00.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,至今為止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:02.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是多麼任性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:06.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天不去粟屋那裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:12.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小 小繪…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:19.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,尾 尾隨我來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:27.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 尾隨你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:29.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:31.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.99,0:13:35.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會這麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:39.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,會這麼喜歡像我這樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:47.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:49.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:50.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:54.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個到底蘊含了多少意義
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:56.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:00.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:04.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:06.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:10.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不明白也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:14.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的 怎麼可能沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:16.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:23.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,卻無法停下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.94,0:14:28.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:32.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得我很可憐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:40.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:42.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不求更多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:44.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小繪…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.81,0:14:45.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:48.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就看不到你的臉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:50.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:52.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都看不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:14:59.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:05.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明直到剛才都沒有跡象
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:08.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對 直到剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明什麼都沒有的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:14.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,會心跳加速嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:15.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:18.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,會的吧 這麼做…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:20.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:22.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我是女生？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:29.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為小繪是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:41.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,會和朋友做這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:44.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和粟屋也做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:51.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 花火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:53.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快要哭了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:54.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,惹哭她了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:58.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭的話就說討厭吧 吶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:01.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:03.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:06.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:08.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡小繪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:12.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:14.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是作為朋友的喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:19.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白我對花火而言是特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:23.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你不想失去我 無法拒絕我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:26.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就要趁虛而入了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:30.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你對我那麼狠心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:34.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果注定得不到你的心意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:36.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,即使只是你的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:38.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想得到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:41.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好好地把我當成替代品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:44.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:49.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:53.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對他說了的話 他會是怎樣的表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:57.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直一直都喜歡著你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:00.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.06,0:17:02.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 又開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:03.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其實
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:07.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,又是無法做到的妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:08.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不存在的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:15.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:19.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴唇好軟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.07,0:17:21.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有甜甜的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:24.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這樣不行 因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:29.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼她是我認識的女生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:31.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:34.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小繪…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:38.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火 告訴我你想怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:39.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,自己說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:42.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:45.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:47.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個就不做了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:51.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不說的話停下來也行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.31,0:17:57.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對舒服的事情沒轍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:17:59.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:02.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被小繪碰觸的話有種…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:05.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有種很舒服的 感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:07.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:11.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:16.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我喜歡花火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:19.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是在觸碰喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:21.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,會傳達這樣的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:23.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才會覺得舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.28,0:18:26.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:30.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,利用我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:32.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來填滿你的所有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:39.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人能給予的溫暖是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:43.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事我明明不可能不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:53.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我卻還是讓小繪完全滿足我的需求
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.27,0:19:02.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在更為寒冷的地方 獨自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:08.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已經無法和小繪變回朋友了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:12.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:14.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你注意到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:19.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天第一次利用了別人的好感
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.58,0:19:23.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和搶走哥哥的那個女人一模一樣的人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:24.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:31.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事 我當然明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:36.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的我不是那個女人的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:40.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙早就察覺到了我的心思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:44.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且有意要踐踏我的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:46.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺得到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:49.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,痛徹心扉一般 從頭澆到腳的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.03,0:19:52.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,作為女人的…優越感
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:20:00.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,既然「現在」的我絕對贏不了她的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:06.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就要改變自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:08.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不管變成什麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.81,0:20:27.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 在生誰的氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:29.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,粟屋？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:30.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,鐘井老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:36.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然你也察覺到了麥的心意了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:41.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:45.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為無法跟憧憬的人交往
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:48.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就找個眼前的同級生交往算了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:50.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:54.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜那兩個人喜歡的都是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.13,0:20:57.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被你不喜歡的男人喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:20:58.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,值得你那麼高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:03.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:07.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明比從男人那裡得到的好感
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.59,0:21:14.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,更令人愉悅的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.22,0:21:17.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:33.57,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}讓我們一起逃離太陽系 在平行線相遇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:48.63,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}如同你我的影子般延伸著 平行線
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:55.10,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}將膽小怯懦歸咎於時代的錯也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:59.47,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}無處可歸的我 找尋著願望的歸所
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:09.35,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}只願成為你唇邊溢出的隻言片語
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.21,0:22:19.82,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}讓我們一起逃離太陽系 在平行線相遇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:30.01,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}帶上無法實現的希冀 以及毫無底氣的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.11,0:22:39.58,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}倘若感情全部流失殆盡 便由我開始描繪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.24,0:22:50.45,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}如今向你我的影子伸出手 平行線
